                    <span>This book promises much, but delivers little. Both the book and the examples from the CD are so full of errors that it is more of an example in frustration than learning. It is nothing more than a usless piece of garbage</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Everything Yet Nothing</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
